snippet.title: Gourmania 2: Great Expectations Gameplay
snippet.description: Gourmania 2: Great Expectations is the sequel to the original Gourmania game from Alawar. Here's a look at the basic gameplay throughout - serving customers, and then fixing up your restaurant(s) between levels.
